name: welcome package
description:
welcome package is giving your 
plants the first taste of 
the florijanna infustions series.

50 ml of glow green will 
nourish green leaf plants, 
living in your apartment. 

50 ml of bloom day support 
and care for your blooming 
plants in the apartment. 

50 ml of wild garden is 
our solution for your 
little wild balcony garden.

name: glow green
description:
glow green is our solution
for green leaf plants, living 
in your apartment. 

Packed in a stylish bottle
you will never need to hide
it away. The fabulous smell
of rainforrest will afloat,
whenever you help to nourish
your plants. 

Just two units per week 
will make all your non 
green plants glow.

name: bloom day
description:
bloom day is our soltion to
care for your blooming plants 
in the apartment. 

Filled in an outstanding bottle 
it fits perfectly next to the 
blossoms of your plants. The 
fresh smell of summerwind
will refresh all your senses 
when you nourish your plants.

Just two units per week
will make all your blooming
plants reach the peak.

name: wild garden
description:
wild garden is our solution
for your little wild balcony 
garden.  

Inside the designed bottle
we packed the finest mix 
of fertilizers to support your 
wild garden. The smell of 
berries gives makes your dive 
in the harvest of your garden.

Just two units per week
will make your wild garden
the center of the balcony.
